picklistValues.masterLabel: 1. Very little impact on the project.
2. Impact will have small change in the project outcome.
3. Event will cause some impact to the project; project can be completed with minimal budget, schedule changes, etc.
4. An event will have a major impact to the project; can complete project but may be over budget, schedule, etc.
5. Very high impact including financial loss, personal injury, termination of contract, loss of client, etc.
